title: Canon Camera Software ISO (CameraWindow, ZoomBrowser EX)
description:
-- Canon ZoomBrowser 5.8EX + Updates --

Includes CameraWindow, MovieEdit, PhotoStitch. RAW Image, and ZoomBrowser EX

-- INSTRUCTIONS --
Burn or Mount the included ISO (CanonDC302W.iso) and install.  
I prefer to use ImgBurn (free, Windows) for burning ISOs.

-- UPDATES --
Included in this torrent are the updates for ZoomBrowser and PhotoStitch which are
available from Canon's website.  It might be a good idea to check there for the 
latest versions.  These are the latest versions as of 03/09/09.

zb621cupd-en: ZoomBrowser EX 6.2.1c Updater
PST3120UPD_EN.exe: PhotoStitch 3.1.20 Updater

-- WHY? --
After losing my install discs for my Canon camera, I found out how difficult 
it was to locate the ZoomBrowser/CameraWindow software.  This torrent is provided 
so you can use the software you PAID for when you bought your camera but 
are unable to get if you ever lose or damage the install disc.

HAPPY SEEDING.

-thevanin
